Dhinaca Abisiniyaanka, safarkii ayaa had iyo jeer ahaa nin aad u hubaysan, badanaana ku jiray ilaa 500 ganacsato ah. Dhoofinta ugu weyn ee Abisiniyanka la xidhiidha Sesea waxay ahayd lo'da, bir iyo cusbo. <ref name="beazly2">{{cite book|last1=Beazley|first1=Charles|title=The Dawn of Modern Geography. A history of exploration and geographical science from the Conversion of the Roman Empire to A.D. 900 (c. A.D. ... of the principal maps of the time.|date=2011|page=210|edition=II}}</ref>


